Dar es Salaam. Tanzania Commission for Universities (TCU) have called for form six leavers and those with certificates obtain from foreign countries, who weren t selected to join higher learning institution to apply as it open the second round of application.According to a statement posted at TCU website the window for second round of application was officially opened on September 12. Those who wish to apply will have until September 23 to apply.Anyone who wishes to apply according to the statement will have to pay Sh50, 000 through Maxmalipo Agents, M-pesa and Tigo pesa.TCU insisted that the minimum admissions qualifications are the same.